Sentencas: Ceramic coatings are being explored to extend the lifetime of stainless steel interconnects in planar Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of (Co,Mn)3O4 coatings on preoxidized stainless steel for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects

Sentencas: One promising coating is Co1.5Mn1.5O4 spinel, which is deposited using various techniques, resulting in different coating thicknesses, compositions and microstructures.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of (Co,Mn)3O4 coatings on preoxidized stainless steel for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects

Sentencas: In this study, stainless steel 441HP samples were subjected to three levels of preoxidation (0, 3, 10 and 100 h in 800 degrees C lab air) prior to coating.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of (Co,Mn)3O4 coatings on preoxidized stainless steel for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects

Sentencas: Samples were coated with 2 mu m CoMn alloy using magnetron sputtering and were subsequently annealed in 800 degrees C air for 0, 10, 100 or 1650 h. Oxidation behaviors were evaluated as a function of these exposures, as well as in dual atmospheres and during area specific resistance (ASR) measurements in 800 degrees C lab air.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of (Co,Mn)3O4 coatings on preoxidized stainless steel for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects

Sentencas: Preoxidation was found to inhibit Fe and Cr transport from the stainless steel into the coating and preoxidized samples exhibited a substantially thinner surface layer after oxidation.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of (Co,Mn)3O4 coatings on preoxidized stainless steel for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects

Sentencas: After ASR testing for 1650 h in 800 degrees C air, the trend of the preoxidized sample values remained level while trend of the non-preoxidized sample values showed an increase.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of (Co,Mn)3O4 coatings on preoxidized stainless steel for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects

Sentencas: Observed oxidation behaviors, their possible mechanisms, and implications for SOFC interconnects are presented and discussed.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of (Co,Mn)3O4 coatings on preoxidized stainless steel for solid oxide fuel cell interconnects
